          <div>
            <img
              src="/Logo/Dark backgrounds/Horizontal/monadicdna-horizontal-darkbg.svg"
              alt="Monadic DNA"
              class="h-8 mb-4"
            />
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">
              Secure, open genomics
